       then the hero grows rather than ever clipping the links. */
    .home-section--hero {
      height: auto;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      overflow: hidden;
      gap: 12px;
      padding-top: 24px; /* tight top padding to save space on mobile */
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
    /* A transformed ancestor hijacks position:fixed — the intro's entrance
       animation ends on a persistent transform, which pinned the heading to
       the section instead of the viewport (the "misaligned top bar"). On
       mobile the container doesn't animate; the columns still fade in. */
    .home-intro--animated {
      animation: none;
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none;
    }

    /* PAGE HEADING — fixed bar, full length (side bar → right edge),
       glass blur, muted full-width border. Identical on every page. */
    .home-intro__header {
      position: fixed !important;
      top: 0 !important;
      left: 44px !important; /* clear the side INDEX bar */
      right: 0 !important;
      z-index: 110 !important;
      background-color: var(--_tokens---color--bg) !important; /* opaque — no glass */
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--_tokens---color--line-soft) !important;
      padding: 16px 12px 14px 12px !important;
      margin: 0 !important;
      box-sizing: border-box !important;
    }
    /* Content starts below the fixed heading (bar ≈52px + 16px gap) */
    .home-section--hero {
      padding-top: 68px;
    }
    .home-intro__label {
      font-size: var(--_tokens---type--small) !important;
      font-weight: 600 !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em !important;
      line-height: 1.2 !important;
      text-transform: none !important;
      color: var(--_tokens---color--fg) !important;
    }
    /* While the Bio is expanded its two paragraphs need room — let the
       hero grow past one screen instead of crushing the photo */
    .home-section--hero:has(.home-intro__body.is-expanded) {
      height: auto;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      overflow: visible;
    }
    .home-section--search {
      overflow-y: visible;
      padding-top: 40px; /* breathing room after the hero's pagination */
    }
    .home-intro__body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    /* Mobile: column 3 is ALWAYS fully visible on load — archive line,
       email, all links, and the Resume/Portfolio downloads. The Bio pill
       only reveals the two bio-paragraph columns above it. */
    .intro-bio-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .home-intro__column--bio {
      display: none;
    }
    .home-intro__body.is-expanded .home-intro__column--bio {
      display: block;
    }
    /* The slider fills whatever height is left under the intro; the photo
       flexes to absorb it, so the whole card (name, photo, facts, dots)
